1
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,960
Your Highness, it's
time for your medicine.

2
00:00:21,190 --> 00:00:21,870
Your Highness?

3
00:00:30,070 --> 00:00:32,030
Your Highness, it's time
for your medicine.

4
00:00:33,350 --> 00:00:34,350
Your Highness, wake up.

5
00:00:44,710 --> 00:00:45,430
Your Highness!

6
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,350
Your Highness!

7
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:47,110
Somebody!

8
00:00:47,390 --> 00:00:48,390
Somebody!

9
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:50,560
Somebody! Get help!

10
00:00:50,790 --> 00:00:51,920
Somebody!

11
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:15,216
=Blossoms of Power=

12
00:02:15,216 --> 00:02:18,060
(Adapted from the novel, After My
Bloom, All Flowers Wither by Jin Huang)

13
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:21,100
=Episode 11=

14
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,470
Your Majesty,

15
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:26,120
Consort Liang died of
blood stasis syndrome.

16
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,560
The illness progresses rapidly.

17
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,240
It can turn fatal within hours.

18
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,310
Your Majesty,

19
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:41,630
blood stasis syndrome can spread miasma.

20
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:44,190
We shouldn't stay here any longer.

21
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,430
Choose an auspicious day.

22
00:02:49,248 --> 00:02:51,552
Lay her to rest in the imperial
mausoleum with full honors.

23
00:02:51,584 --> 00:02:52,512
Yes, Your Majesty.

24
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:04,560
Father.

25
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,560
I ask for your permission

26
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:09,960
to let me keep vigil
at my mother's tomb.

27
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,750
Your mother came from a distant land.

28
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,080
You're the only child she left behind.

29
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,280
If she's watching from the afterlife,

30
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:20,150
she would not want to see
you waste away like this.

31
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,520
Stay here

32
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,910
with your grandmother and me instead.

33
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,030
Thank you for your concern, Father,

34
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,430
but I have no other wish in life

35
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:33,190
than to fulfill my filial
duty at Mother's tomb.

36
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,710
Please grant me this wish, Father.

37
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:42,280
I never would've expected this.

38
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,280
Mo Yuan was investigating
Consort Liang's crimes,

39
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,800
and now she's suddenly dead.

40
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,000
I originally thought

41
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,030
she was taking revenge
on me for her brother, Ye Qi.

42
00:03:50,512 --> 00:03:51,960
But now that she's died so suddenly,

43
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,310
someone must've silenced her.

44
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,630
Your Highness, are you saying

45
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,030
this wasn't a coincidence?

46
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,310
Your Highness,

47
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,560
I'm back.

48
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:03,360
There's no one even in charge

49
00:04:03,470 --> 00:04:05,190
of Consort Liang's Yilan Palace now.

50
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,120
It's complete chaos.

51
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,680
The Sixth Prince is rather strange, too.

52
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:10,030
You could say he's a devoted son,

53
00:04:10,030 --> 00:04:11,590
but he didn't shed a single tear.

54
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,080
Yet you can't call him unfilial either,

55
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,864
since he volunteered to guard her tomb.

56
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,160
Was there anything unusual

57
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,608
before Consort Liang's sudden death?

58
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:19,430
Yes.

59
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,120
She was scratched by a cat.

60
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,950
She applied a certain hand balm.

61
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,750
I secretly brought some back.

62
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:34,240
This balm contains cold fern.

63
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:36,000
It smells sweet to humans,

64
00:04:36,270 --> 00:04:38,120
but it drives cats and
dogs into a frenzy.

65
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,800
Consort Liang was scratched

66
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,232
because she was wearing this balm.

67
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,510
Someone must've

68
00:04:43,510 --> 00:04:44,912
coated the cat's claws with poison.

69
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,270
Your Highness, who do you suspect?

70
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:47,310
Noble Consort Rong.

71
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:50,070
She once ordered Lady Hu to harm you.

72
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:53,120
Noble Consort Rong and
Consort Liang both have sons.

73
00:04:53,296 --> 00:04:55,008
Naturally, they saw
each other as rivals.

74
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,000
Everyone in this palace

75
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,240
hides behind layer
upon layer of deception.

76
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:01,000
One careless mistake,

77
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,310
and you're finished.

78
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,480
It's impossible to
guard against everyone.

79
00:05:06,190 --> 00:05:08,120
Fortunately, you and the Crown Prince

80
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,560
have decided to stand together

81
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,480
through whatever comes.

82
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,630
I really should thank him for that.

83
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:17,680
Tian Yuan,

84
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,360
don't you think

85
00:05:19,696 --> 00:05:21,872
there's something suspicious
about Consort Liang's death?

86
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,000
Your Highness,

87
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,600
the imperial physician said
it was blood stasis syndrome,

88
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,950
but I think

89
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,800
she was more likely poisoned.

90
00:05:28,912 --> 00:05:31,952
There aren't many poisons that
could fool the Imperial Medical Office.

91
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,750
It reminds me of the person
who poisoned me.

92
00:05:36,190 --> 00:05:38,070
You mean the person
who killed Consort Liang

93
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,360
and the one who poisoned you

94
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,680
could be the same person?

95
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,870
Their methods are similar,

96
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:45,488
and both culprits are hidden
deep within the palace.

97
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,830
That's exactly what I suspect.

98
00:05:47,072 --> 00:05:48,560
There's something else strange, too.

99
00:05:48,688 --> 00:05:50,480
That foreign merchant
who sold the poison

100
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,160
seems to have vanished into thin air.

101
00:05:52,192 --> 00:05:53,760
There's no trace of him anywhere.

102
00:05:54,416 --> 00:05:56,190
Send all the clues
related to Consort Liang

103
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,920
to Zhao Zhenghao,

104
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,430
Cui Jinbai, and Hua Fuhai as well.

105
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,024
Yes, Your Highness.

106
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,430
Speak.

107
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,680
I heard

108
00:06:13,680 --> 00:06:16,750
Commandery Princess Zhaoning's brother,
Shen Yun'an,

109
00:06:16,768 --> 00:06:18,500
has asked permission
to come to the capital.

110
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:19,920
He and the Duke of Wei

111
00:06:20,016 --> 00:06:22,672
don't seem to approve of
your marriage to Her Highness.

112
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,390
Good. Let him come.

113
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,560
Then he can see for himself

114
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,680
exactly what kind of man I am.

115
00:06:32,928 --> 00:06:33,950
He's bound to like me.

116
00:06:42,112 --> 00:06:44,120
Young Master will be arriving
in the capital soon.

117
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,510
Everyone, be on your best behavior.

118
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:46,560
- Yes.
- Yes.

119
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,720
Your Highness.

120
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,560
I haven't seen my brother in so long.

121
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,430
I wonder what his
temper's like these days.

122
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:00,480
Your Highness,

123
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,630
you said it yourself.

124
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:03,600
Young Master's always
been straightforward,

125
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,070
a true man of the northwest.

126
00:07:05,216 --> 00:07:06,950
You've only been in
the capital for a while.

127
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:09,040
His temper couldn't
have changed that quickly.

128
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:09,830
That's true.

129
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:11,870
Zhen Zhu,

130
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,190
you know my brother's habits well.

131
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:15,630
Keep a close eye on them.

132
00:07:16,144 --> 00:07:17,488
Don't worry, Your Highness.

133
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,560
Young Master has an old leg injury.

134
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,896
It flares up whenever he gets cold.

135
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,270
This quilt's too thin.

136
00:07:24,270 --> 00:07:25,120
Bring a thicker one.

137
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:25,920
- Yes.
- Yes.

138
00:07:25,984 --> 00:07:27,720
Young Master likes
to take big gulps of tea.

139
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,070
This cup's too small.

140
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,510
Bring out the jade tea set

141
00:07:30,510 --> 00:07:32,512
with the evergreen pine
design from the storeroom.

142
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,160
Young Master enjoys
reading military texts.

143
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,330
Place those books on warfare

144
00:07:35,344 --> 00:07:36,928
somewhere within easy reach in his room.

145
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,630
Three,

146
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:40,560
two,

147
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:41,560
one,

148
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:42,240
run!

149
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,430
Yun'an,

150
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,360
I won!

151
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,950
Your Highness.

152
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:06,870
Your Highness.

153
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,720
What's wrong?

154
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,680
I miss my brother a little.

155
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,920
Don't worry, Your Highness.

156
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:16,240
I'll take care of everything here.

157
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:17,680
Your Highness,

158
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:20,160
why don't you think about
how to thank the Crown Prince?

159
00:08:21,616 --> 00:08:24,224
His Highness seems to be quite
fond of experimenting with pastries.

160
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:26,190
Every time you visit the East Palace,

161
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:28,120
he has snacks prepared in advance,

162
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,310
and they're never the same.

163
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:31,240
He must be quite the foodie.

164
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,000
He should eat something
that's easy to digest.

165
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,390
I'll make him a bowl
of delicate wontons.

166
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:39,840
You're thinking about Crown Prince
more and more these days.

167
00:08:42,624 --> 00:08:44,752
Your Highness, you helped
me solve Consort Liang's case.

168
00:08:44,816 --> 00:08:46,496
I didn't know how else to repay you.

169
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,840
You made these wontons yourself?

170
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,320
You're still in poor health.

171
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:53,510
Eating too much could
upset your stomach,

172
00:08:53,552 --> 00:08:54,950
so I only served you a small portion.

173
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,870
I never expected

174
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,550
I'd be lucky enough
to taste your cooking.

175
00:08:57,600 --> 00:09:01,620
(Auspicious Blessings)

176
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,360
They're tender and silky,

177
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,120
with a wonderful lingering flavor.

178
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,960
Whenever anyone else makes them,

179
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,270
I always find them too greasy.

180
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,910
But yours

181
00:09:35,550 --> 00:09:36,600
are just right.

182
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:40,360
Three wasn't nearly enough.

183
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:42,840
I'll have the kitchen
prepare the same filling.

184
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,120
Would you

185
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,480
make them for me again?

186
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:47,630
All right.

187
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,510
There's a legend in northwest.

188
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,030
Hundun was once a vicious ancient beast,

189
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:10,720
bloodthirsty and cruel,
bringing suffering to the world

190
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,320
and leaving the people no peace.

191
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:14,320
It's said that eating wontons
named after it

192
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,960
can ward off evil and misfortune,

193
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,360
and bring peace,

194
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,320
good fortune, and safety.

195
00:10:21,584 --> 00:10:23,216
Thank you for such
a thoughtful gesture.

196
00:10:30,790 --> 00:10:32,000
Speaking of northwest,

197
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,480
Your Highness, what do you think

198
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,360
of the Northwest Army?

199
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,790
Why do you ask?

200
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,270
Some say

201
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:43,670
the Northwest Army is the pillar
that keeps the realm secure.

202
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,150
Others say

203
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,630
the Duke of Wei holds enough power

204
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,200
to carve out a kingdom of his own,

205
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,750
so civil and military authority
should be divided.

206
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,630
What do you think?

207
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,440
To govern the northwest,

208
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:59,870
you need a strong army
to repel foreign enemies,

209
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:02,080
and sound governance
to keep the rear secure.

210
00:11:02,670 --> 00:11:04,200
Every one of those tasks

211
00:11:04,304 --> 00:11:06,240
requires civil and military
power to work as one.

212
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:07,600
If they're divided,

213
00:11:08,064 --> 00:11:09,510
they'll only hold each other back,

214
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,184
and the northwest will never be stable.

215
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,080
You're a Crown Prince of great insight

216
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:15,720
and ambition.

217
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,150
When you take the throne,

218
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,720
Daxing will surely enjoy
lasting peace and prosperity.

219
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:24,750
I'll remember

220
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,910
everything that matters to you.

221
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,440
Your family

222
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,960
will remain safe,

223
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,270
and the northwest

224
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,550
will know peace.

225
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,000
Can you promise me that?

226
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:35,720
I can.

227
00:11:40,768 --> 00:11:42,030
But I don't trust anyone else,

228
00:11:42,750 --> 00:11:44,320
nor will I place my family's lives

229
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:45,600
in someone else's hands.

230
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,600
What a coincidence.

231
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,720
Neither will I.

232
00:11:53,750 --> 00:11:55,600
Then let's choose to trust ourselves.

233
00:11:56,150 --> 00:11:58,600
If we succeed, it'll be
because we were more capable,

234
00:11:58,672 --> 00:11:59,940
and we'll have nothing to regret.

235
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,550
If we fail, it'll be
because we were outmatched,

236
00:12:02,672 --> 00:12:04,112
and we'll accept the consequences.

237
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:22,060
(Sixian Hall)

238
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,080
It's windy outside.

239
00:12:23,168 --> 00:12:24,816
You needn't see me out, Your Highness.

240
00:12:25,264 --> 00:12:26,576
Take care, Your Highness.

241
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:54,670
Xihe.

242
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,720
I can see colors now.

243
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:04,270
That's wonderful.

244
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:05,520
Congratulations, Your Highness.

245
00:13:06,390 --> 00:13:07,550
Now that my eyes have healed,

246
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,080
are you

247
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:11,030
even a little happy for me?

248
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:34,540
(Sixian Hall)

249
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:48,620
(Shen Yun'an, Heir to the Duke of Wei)

250
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:49,790
Who is that young master?

251
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,120
He carries himself with such poise.

252
00:13:51,390 --> 00:13:52,320
Young Master Shen.

253
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,740
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

254
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,200
He's here.

255
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:28,832
- Greetings, Young Master.
- Greetings, Young Master.

256
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:30,750
Yun'an.

257
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:41,870
Let me get a good look at you.

258
00:14:42,336 --> 00:14:43,808
My little sister's even prettier now.

259
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,000
And you've

260
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,080
gotten a little tanned.

261
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:49,910
You little tease.

262
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,200
Uncle Qing,

263
00:14:51,328 --> 00:14:52,320
it's been a long time.

264
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,550
Greetings, Young Master.

265
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:55,390
Yun'an,

266
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,240
your room is ready.

267
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,440
Let's go inside and talk.

268
00:14:59,320 --> 00:14:59,750
All right.

269
00:15:05,540 --> 00:15:08,140
(Duke of Wei's Manor)

270
00:15:16,816 --> 00:15:18,840
You've been in the capital
for quite some time now.

271
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,000
Father's been worried
sick about your marriage.

272
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:23,120
When the Anxi defense map went missing,

273
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:25,720
I heard Prince Lie used
it to ask for your hand.

274
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:27,808
That left Father with a
poor impression of him.

275
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:28,512
But I think

276
00:15:28,528 --> 00:15:31,460
the fact that he risked execution for
deceiving the emperor to help our family

277
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,080
proves how deeply he cares for you.

278
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:33,960
Yun'an,

279
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,200
Prince Lie isn't the
man I want to marry.

280
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:40,200
Such a spirited young man,

281
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,910
willing to risk everything
to protect you...

282
00:15:42,256 --> 00:15:43,984
You truly don't have feelings for him?

283
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:49,510
Then, among all the princes,

284
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:51,080
who exactly have you chosen?

285
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,150
The Crown Prince.

286
00:15:55,936 --> 00:15:58,208
Everyone knows he's been frail and
sickly since childhood,

287
00:15:58,256 --> 00:15:59,550
as fragile as a willow branch.

288
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:00,848
He's hardly an ideal husband.

289
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:02,270
Why him?

290
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:05,390
His character and temperament

291
00:16:05,550 --> 00:16:06,720
are exactly what I admire.

292
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:09,320
And precisely because he's frail,

293
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:10,510
he won't try to dominate me.

294
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:12,390
Compared to a capable, forceful man,

295
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:15,480
I'd rather have a husband who's
obedient and easy to handle.

296
00:16:15,550 --> 00:16:17,200
That way, life will be
much more peaceful.

297
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,480
So you've chosen him

298
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:21,480
because he's frail and easy to control?

299
00:16:26,870 --> 00:16:28,030
Did someone hurt you?

300
00:16:29,600 --> 00:16:30,960
If someone had,

301
00:16:31,150 --> 00:16:33,344
do you think I'd still be
sitting here safe and sound?

302
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:36,150
That wicked servant Ling Long

303
00:16:36,150 --> 00:16:37,824
pushed you into the river
on Xiao's orders.

304
00:16:37,856 --> 00:16:39,750
Father and I were beside
ourselves with worry.

305
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:41,840
We only felt relieved
when we heard you were unharmed.

306
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:45,360
You faced such danger
the moment you arrived.

307
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,550
After coming to the capital,

308
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:49,630
did all the scheming
here frighten you so much

309
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:51,510
that now you only want
security, not true love?

310
00:16:51,910 --> 00:16:52,750
If that's the case,

311
00:16:52,816 --> 00:16:54,030
you should return to northwest.

312
00:16:54,048 --> 00:16:55,880
I'll stay in the capital
and marry a princess.

313
00:16:55,904 --> 00:16:56,560
No.

314
00:16:57,910 --> 00:16:59,440
I know you want to protect me.

315
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,510
But if you marry a princess,

316
00:17:01,510 --> 00:17:03,360
you'll have to surrender
your military command.

317
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:04,960
You were born to be a great general.

318
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,750
The lives of tens of thousands
in northwest depend on you.

319
00:17:07,808 --> 00:17:09,520
You can't let your talent go to waste.

320
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:14,310
I only want you to live well

321
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:16,310
and be happy every day.

322
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:25,960
You've had a long, exhausting journey.

323
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,200
Get some rest first.

324
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:28,656
I'll go to the kitchen

325
00:17:28,656 --> 00:17:30,270
and make a few of your favorite dishes.

326
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:33,750
Xihe.

327
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:36,640
You've changed.

328
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,640
You're not as timid as you used to be.

329
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:40,030
There's a spark in your eyes now

330
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:42,030
that I never saw back in northwest.

331
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:45,000
Could it really be because
of the Crown Prince?

332
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,680
Of course. It's because I'm in love.

333
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:55,500
(East Palace)

334
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:00,680
Your Highness.

335
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:09,632
Please take a seat.

336
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:40,000
I grew this tea myself.

337
00:18:40,384 --> 00:18:42,464
I hope it's to your liking,
Young Master Shen.

338
00:19:00,720 --> 00:19:02,590
A man should set his
sights on greater things,

339
00:19:02,608 --> 00:19:05,070
yet you have time to grow tea.

340
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:06,680
I'm a straightforward man,

341
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,480
so forgive me for asking,

342
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:11,640
but do you have consumption?

343
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,000
Seriously?

344
00:19:14,128 --> 00:19:16,160
I only suffer from coughing
and shortness of breath.

345
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:17,880
If I had consumption,

346
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:18,880
do you think

347
00:19:18,928 --> 00:19:20,912
they'd still let me
remain in the palace?

348
00:19:23,350 --> 00:19:24,720
Though some time ago,

349
00:19:25,790 --> 00:19:27,070
I did develop an eye condition.

350
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:29,550
Thankfully, Commandery Princess
went to great lengths

351
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:30,920
to find treatment for me.

352
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:32,590
So you're not only frail,

353
00:19:32,624 --> 00:19:34,464
but you had trouble with your eyes, too?

354
00:19:34,528 --> 00:19:35,696
Don't worry, Young Master Shen.

355
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:38,110
Her Highness found a physician for me,

356
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:38,976
and I've recovered.

357
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:40,750
Here in the palace,

358
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,880
everyone else avoids me.

359
00:19:42,270 --> 00:19:43,200
Only Her Highness

360
00:19:43,264 --> 00:19:44,624
is willing to stay close to me.

361
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,500
She worried I'd be
sensitive to the cold,

362
00:19:47,792 --> 00:19:49,440
so she blended an incense
to keep me warm.

363
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,110
She worried I had no appetite,

364
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,480
so she made me wontons.

365
00:19:52,816 --> 00:19:54,432
She even comes to
the East Palace often

366
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,480
to visit me.

367
00:19:57,830 --> 00:19:58,880
Why aren't you eating?

368
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,640
Do you think my pastries

369
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:01,680
aren't any good?

370
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,750
Youyou has always been like this.

371
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,640
She can never turn her
back on someone in need.

372
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,110
So Her Highness's childhood name

373
00:20:23,510 --> 00:20:24,350
is Youyou.

374
00:20:28,816 --> 00:20:30,270
We must be destined for each other.

375
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,510
My childhood name

376
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:32,750
is Luming.

377
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:35,830
How did I never know

378
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,440
His Highness had a childhood name?

379
00:20:38,448 --> 00:20:40,240
As for whether you're
destined for each other,

380
00:20:40,320 --> 00:20:42,270
it's far too soon to say, Your Highness.

381
00:20:42,270 --> 00:20:43,720
I believe persistence will be rewarded.

382
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:44,880
I'm in love with Youyou.

383
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:45,880
Your Highness,

384
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:48,550
you should call my sister Zhaoning.

385
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:51,590
Otherwise, your declaration of
love may seem rather frivolous.

386
00:20:53,350 --> 00:20:55,110
I've never been in love before.

387
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,720
All I know is

388
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:59,350
the moment I wake up,

389
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:01,400
I want to see her right away.

390
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,480
Even in my sleep,

391
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,160
I dream of her.

392
00:21:05,808 --> 00:21:07,648
Whenever I see something wonderful,

393
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,510
I want to give it to her at once.

394
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:14,030
It's only been a month or two.

395
00:21:14,128 --> 00:21:15,728
You couldn't have loved her so deeply.

396
00:21:15,872 --> 00:21:17,472
Love begins before you even realize it,

397
00:21:18,016 --> 00:21:19,480
and then grows deeper and deeper.

398
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,110
By the time I noticed,

399
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:23,000
it had taken root in my heart.

400
00:21:25,830 --> 00:21:28,070
And what if my sister
has no feelings for you?

401
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,680
I'd swear on my life

402
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:30,880
to protect her forever.

403
00:21:31,968 --> 00:21:33,440
You'll have no regret or resentment

404
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:34,768
even if your love is unrequited?

405
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:38,070
It would only mean I hadn't done enough.

406
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,350
Even then, I'd have no regrets.

407
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:45,240
Darn it.

408
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,110
How could I have

409
00:21:46,110 --> 00:21:47,590
let Xihe's childhood name slip?

410
00:21:47,856 --> 00:21:49,350
Now he's using it to get close to her.

411
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:52,030
He's glib, shamelessly cheesy.

412
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:54,592
The more I look at him,
the less trustworthy he seems.

413
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:57,000
My innocent little sister

414
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,680
must've been fooled
by that handsome face.

415
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,440
No. I can't allow this.

416
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,640
(Prince Ding's Manor)
Hurry up.

417
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:25,160
All right.

418
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:25,550
Go ahead.

419
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:28,510
Let me do it.

420
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:29,640
You?

421
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:34,510
Watch me.

422
00:22:34,790 --> 00:22:36,110
That's beautifully written.

423
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:37,480
Bull's-eye!

424
00:22:38,030 --> 00:22:38,940
- Good!
- Good!

425
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:45,160
Is this how things are
always done in the capital?

426
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:47,200
The chrysanthemums have merely bloomed,

427
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,928
yet they're holding
such a lavish banquet

428
00:22:49,030 --> 00:22:50,224
and inviting so many guests.

429
00:22:50,352 --> 00:22:52,440
Prince Ding's chrysanthemum
garden is quite famous.

430
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:54,270
They hold a viewing banquet every year.

431
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:02,000
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

432
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:09,030
Your Highness, you're here
for the banquet, too?

433
00:23:09,664 --> 00:23:12,070
Staying cooped up in the palace
all day is terribly dull.

434
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:13,110
Changtai invited me,

435
00:23:13,168 --> 00:23:14,704
so I came out for a change of scenery.

436
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:18,030
This entrance is
reserved for the ladies.

437
00:23:18,110 --> 00:23:19,504
The male guests enter over there.

438
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:20,510
Your Highness,

439
00:23:20,510 --> 00:23:21,440
let's go in together.

440
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,400
With my health...

441
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:25,160
I've never really fit
in with the other men.

442
00:23:25,550 --> 00:23:28,350
I've always preferred
spending time with the ladies.

443
00:23:28,784 --> 00:23:30,432
You go ahead, Young Master Shen.

444
00:23:30,510 --> 00:23:31,790
I'll go in with Her Highness.

445
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,030
Unless...

446
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,830
you'd rather go in with the ladies, too?

447
00:23:37,830 --> 00:23:39,424
Then the three of us can go together.

448
00:23:40,480 --> 00:23:41,110
No need.

449
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,200
After you, Your Highness.

450
00:23:51,830 --> 00:23:53,510
Please wait,
Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

451
00:23:58,750 --> 00:23:59,790
(Gu Qingshu?)

452
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:03,310
Greetings, Your Highness.

453
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,832
Greetings, Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

454
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:05,720
County Princess Liyang,

455
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:06,680
how may we help you?

456
00:24:06,830 --> 00:24:08,070
Your Highness,

457
00:24:08,350 --> 00:24:09,640
my brother-in-law told me

458
00:24:09,888 --> 00:24:11,296
that before my sister passed away,

459
00:24:11,300 --> 00:24:13,808
she and Her Highness were
close friends who exchanged letters.

460
00:24:13,824 --> 00:24:15,160
My sister was quiet by nature

461
00:24:15,160 --> 00:24:16,624
and rarely socialized with anyone.

462
00:24:16,656 --> 00:24:17,920
I'm truly grateful to you

463
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:19,550
for being such a dear friend to her.

464
00:24:20,030 --> 00:24:21,160
She's gone now.

465
00:24:21,216 --> 00:24:23,392
There's no need to thank me,
County Princess Liyang.

466
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:26,270
Your Highness,

467
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:28,400
it gets very windy in the capital
this time of year.

468
00:24:28,830 --> 00:24:30,550
I happen to have a hand warmer with me.

469
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:32,440
Please take it,

470
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:33,270
if you don't mind...

471
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,640
I've overstepped.

472
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,480
Zhaoning,

473
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:46,680
of course His Highness
would take good care of you.

474
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:53,310
Let's go in together.

475
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:04,390
His Highness is rather
particular about cleanliness.

476
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:06,880
He's not used to Her Highness
using other people's things.

477
00:25:06,976 --> 00:25:09,030
Please don't take offense,
County Princess Liyang.

478
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,440
The Gu family's second daughter

479
00:25:16,496 --> 00:25:18,048
isn't someone to be underestimated.

480
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:20,750
Look at this one.

481
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:22,680
It's beautiful.

482
00:25:23,110 --> 00:25:24,350
This one's such a lovely color.

483
00:25:24,464 --> 00:25:25,510
And it smells wonderful.

484
00:25:32,256 --> 00:25:33,960
There are all sorts
of people here today.

485
00:25:34,070 --> 00:25:35,720
Be sure to watch everyone carefully.

486
00:25:36,256 --> 00:25:38,030
Thank you for the warning,
Your Highness.

487
00:25:38,310 --> 00:25:39,350
Let's go look over there.

488
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,000
All right.

489
00:25:40,510 --> 00:25:41,400
Take a look.

490
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:47,200
Xihe.

491
00:25:48,030 --> 00:25:49,400
That's Prince Ding's Consort,

492
00:25:49,510 --> 00:25:50,310
Li Yanhui.

493
00:25:54,016 --> 00:25:55,790
Please take your seat
first, Your Highness.

494
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:56,920
I'll be right back.

495
00:25:57,168 --> 00:25:58,000
I'll wait for you.

496
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,200
Greetings, Your Highness.

497
00:26:09,550 --> 00:26:10,680
Greetings, Your Highness.

498
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:12,000
Greetings, Your Highness.

499
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:15,200
Greetings, Your Highness.

500
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,830
A grown man,

501
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:18,790
openly mingling with the ladies,

502
00:26:19,590 --> 00:26:20,880
grinning from ear to ear.

503
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,000
Has he no sense of propriety?

504
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,830
Young Master Shen.

505
00:26:27,680 --> 00:26:28,640
Prince Lie.

506
00:26:37,310 --> 00:26:37,830
Young Master.

507
00:26:37,830 --> 00:26:39,030
I'm a straightforward man,

508
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,070
so I'll speak plainly.

509
00:26:40,576 --> 00:26:42,450
When it came to choosing a husband
for my sister,

510
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,830
Father and I originally favored you.

511
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:46,550
But after what happened
with the defense map,

512
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:48,750
Father became
somewhat displeased with you.

513
00:26:49,110 --> 00:26:50,480
I acted rashly

514
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,590
and offended Her Highness.

515
00:26:52,270 --> 00:26:54,590
I let both the Duke of Wei and you down.

516
00:26:54,736 --> 00:26:56,310
You needn't dwell on it, Your Highness.

517
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,720
At court,

518
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,640
you risked your life for our family.

519
00:26:59,776 --> 00:27:01,750
How could I not know
your feelings are sincere?

520
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:04,030
You're brave and
accomplished, Prince Lie.

521
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:06,880
You're far more impressive

522
00:27:07,030 --> 00:27:08,110
than that sickly weakling.

523
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:09,750
I still think

524
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,240
you and my sister

525
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,110
are the best match.

526
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:16,350
I haven't won Her Highness's heart.

527
00:27:16,864 --> 00:27:18,960
That only means I haven't
done nearly enough.

528
00:27:19,744 --> 00:27:20,960
Don't worry, Your Highness.

529
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,830
As long as Xihe agrees,

530
00:27:22,830 --> 00:27:24,224
Father will never stand in your way.

531
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,720
If you still wish to marry her,

532
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:26,160
I...

533
00:27:26,270 --> 00:27:28,030
Her Highness is the only lady I love.

534
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:30,200
My resolve to marry her

535
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,000
is unshakable.

536
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:34,750
Good.

537
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:36,200
Let's have another drink.

538
00:27:36,550 --> 00:27:37,030
All right.

539
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,750
Try this one.

540
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:40,440
It's quite good.

541
00:27:40,550 --> 00:27:41,750
Come on, have another drink.

542
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,200
It really is good.

543
00:27:44,550 --> 00:27:46,110
Greetings, Princess Ding.

544
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:49,820
(Li Yanhui, Princess Ding)

545
00:27:49,830 --> 00:27:51,700
There's no need to stand
on ceremony with me.

546
00:27:51,728 --> 00:27:53,344
I'm not one
of your empire's noble ladies.

547
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:55,510
I've no patience for all
your rules and etiquette.

548
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:00,680
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
is of noble birth.

549
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:04,240
His Majesty is personally
choosing a husband for her.

550
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:06,680
What other lady could
receive such an honor?

551
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:08,110
Princess Ding,

552
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:10,310
why are you treating her this way?

553
00:28:17,696 --> 00:28:20,070
You've only just gone from
death-row prisoner to titled lady,

554
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:22,590
and already you're rushing
to curry favor with everyone?

555
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,790
The Gu family produced a daughter

556
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:26,224
as proud and unyielding as Gu Qingzhi.

557
00:28:26,304 --> 00:28:28,580
How did they end up raising a
spineless sycophant like you?

558
00:28:29,376 --> 00:28:31,440
You disrespected
Commandery Princess Zhaoning first,

559
00:28:31,584 --> 00:28:33,200
and now you're mocking me in public.

560
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:34,640
Li Yanhui,

561
00:28:34,912 --> 00:28:36,880
you don't
still think you're a princess, do you?

562
00:28:37,550 --> 00:28:38,880
Nanzhou has fallen.

563
00:28:39,104 --> 00:28:41,024
If it weren't
for His Majesty's arranged marriage,

564
00:28:41,030 --> 00:28:42,992
and Prince Ding agreed
to take you as his wife,

565
00:28:43,040 --> 00:28:44,704
do you think you would have survived?

566
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:54,790
I told you,

567
00:28:54,790 --> 00:28:55,590
be careful.

568
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:57,960
Prince Lie,

569
00:28:58,240 --> 00:29:00,440
did you see how Crown Prince
moved just now?

570
00:29:00,750 --> 00:29:03,070
Wasn't he supposed
to have no martial arts skills?

571
00:29:03,790 --> 00:29:05,160
What's going on?

572
00:29:16,310 --> 00:29:17,070
Make way.

573
00:29:23,940 --> 00:29:26,140
(Xiao Changtai, Fourth Prince,
Prince Ding)

574
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:27,310
Greetings, Your Highness.

575
00:29:30,432 --> 00:29:32,528
I'm sorry you were
frightened just now, Your Highness.

576
00:29:32,576 --> 00:29:34,224
I failed to look after
my guests properly.

577
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:35,550
Please forgive me.

578
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,550
Yanyan.

579
00:29:47,152 --> 00:29:48,200
County Princess Liyang

580
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,240
is the lady Father
intends for Changqing.

581
00:29:52,750 --> 00:29:54,550
Your family's affairs
are none of my concern.

582
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,310
She started this,

583
00:29:57,590 --> 00:29:59,110
so I've no reason to let her off.

584
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:00,440
If I don't

585
00:30:01,030 --> 00:30:02,750
carve a mark across her face today

586
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:04,070
and let her taste the consequences,

587
00:30:04,080 --> 00:30:05,570
she'll dare to
do worse in the future!

588
00:30:05,580 --> 00:30:07,030
I'm a lady personally
ennobled by His Majesty!

589
00:30:07,030 --> 00:30:07,750
So what?

590
00:30:07,750 --> 00:30:08,480
Enough.

591
00:30:08,480 --> 00:30:09,030
Yanyan,

592
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,400
calm down.

593
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,750
You're trying to stop me?

594
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,160
It's only a face.

595
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,640
Is it really that important?

596
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:34,110
It's just one cut.

597
00:30:34,560 --> 00:30:35,550
It won't kill anyone.

598
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:40,110
Yanyan!

599
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:58,160
Your Highness,

600
00:30:58,920 --> 00:30:59,960
why are you doing this?

601
00:31:00,510 --> 00:31:03,240
You used me
to provoke Princess Ding

602
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,590
and cause trouble.

603
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:06,550
If I had been cut
by these porcelain shards,

604
00:31:06,830 --> 00:31:08,350
would that have been what you wanted?

605
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,200
It was only an accident.

606
00:31:12,110 --> 00:31:13,640
I may be of low status,

607
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,110
but I won't let you

608
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,510
humiliate me like this.

609
00:31:16,510 --> 00:31:17,350
Humiliate you?

610
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:19,400
I merely told the truth.

611
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,688
And you call that humiliation?

612
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,160
It seems you don't know

613
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:23,640
what true humiliation feels like.

614
00:31:24,790 --> 00:31:25,440
Mo Yu.

615
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,550
Your Highness,

616
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,550
you're the highest-ranking person here.

617
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:47,480
You saw everything that happened today.

618
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:50,030
Please judge this matter

619
00:31:50,830 --> 00:31:52,070
and clear my name.

620
00:31:57,480 --> 00:31:58,920
Commandery Princess Zhaoning is

621
00:31:59,510 --> 00:32:00,720
gentle and sweet by nature.

622
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:03,240
After what happened today,

623
00:32:04,080 --> 00:32:05,550
she must've been terribly frightened.

624
00:32:05,830 --> 00:32:07,400
You're all well-bred young ladies,

625
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:09,000
so please look out for her.

626
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,750
Don't let anyone with ill intentions
get near her

627
00:32:12,070 --> 00:32:13,070
and frighten her again.

628
00:32:17,648 --> 00:32:19,550
They have your favorite
peach blossom drink.

629
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:21,110
Let's go have some to calm your nerves.

630
00:32:26,550 --> 00:32:27,310
Your Highness,

631
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:29,640
my sister's usually not like this.

632
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,720
Whenever she's with Huayong,

633
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:35,350
she's always so free-spirited.

634
00:32:36,384 --> 00:32:37,990
So this is what you
people in the capital

635
00:32:38,110 --> 00:32:39,480
call free-spirited?

636
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,790
Your Highness.

637
00:33:12,976 --> 00:33:13,880
How are you feeling?

638
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:15,400
Any better?

639
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,000
Brother-in-law,

640
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,030
I don't even know

641
00:33:18,030 --> 00:33:19,888
how I offended
Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

642
00:33:21,790 --> 00:33:23,400
She was utterly ruthless.

643
00:33:23,552 --> 00:33:25,830
With the Crown Prince taking her side,
she fears nothing.

644
00:33:26,688 --> 00:33:29,088
Commandery Princess Zhaoning
is as broad-minded as any man.

645
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:31,790
She'd never hold a grudge
over something trivial.

646
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,750
What exactly did you do?

647
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:37,590
Brother-in-law,

648
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,830
I'm your sister-in-law,

649
00:33:39,830 --> 00:33:41,510
yet you're taking Shen Xihe's side?

650
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:44,400
After what she did to me,

651
00:33:44,496 --> 00:33:45,960
aren't you going to stand up for me?

652
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,110
From now on,

653
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:50,480
stay away from
Commandery Princess Zhaoning.

654
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:52,510
Saving you

655
00:33:53,110 --> 00:33:54,350
was the last thing I could do

656
00:33:55,070 --> 00:33:56,920
for your sister and the Gu family.

657
00:33:57,248 --> 00:33:58,480
If you think that gives you

658
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:00,480
the freedom to do as you please,

659
00:34:01,952 --> 00:34:03,510
don't blame me for showing no mercy.

660
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:23,710
Your Majesty, please bestow
upon him his courtesy name.

661
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,880
Now that the rites are complete,

662
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,800
on this auspicious day,

663
00:35:34,150 --> 00:35:35,760
I hereby bestow upon you

664
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:38,710
the courtesy name Beichen.

665
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,480
Thank you, Your Majesty.

666
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:53,440
"To govern by virtue
is like the North Star,

667
00:35:53,472 --> 00:35:56,320
steadfast in its place while all
the other stars revolve around it."

668
00:35:56,880 --> 00:35:59,400
His Majesty has clearly decided

669
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:01,030
to pass the throne to the Crown Prince.

670
00:36:05,230 --> 00:36:06,230
Rise.

671
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,840
Trying to pledge your allegiance now

672
00:36:23,070 --> 00:36:24,630
is a little premature.

673
00:36:26,320 --> 00:36:27,280
Huayong,

674
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:29,190
the ceremony is over.

675
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:33,070
You should return to
the East Palace and get some rest.

676
00:36:33,120 --> 00:36:35,030
I still need to pay my respects
to our brothers.

677
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:37,440
I appreciate the thought,

678
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:38,630
but...

679
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,190
given your health,

680
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,070
you may skip

681
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:43,320
these formalities.

682
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:44,880
Minister of Rites.

683
00:36:45,216 --> 00:36:47,408
Now that the coming-of-age ceremony
is complete,

684
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:50,070
tomorrow, all the civil
and military officials,

685
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:52,920
along with the imperial
princes and royal kinsmen,

686
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:56,550
shall gather at Qinzheng Hall

687
00:36:56,550 --> 00:36:59,030
to perform the fourfold ceremonial
bow before the Crown Prince.

688
00:37:09,150 --> 00:37:09,670
Xihe,

689
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:11,320
I'm going to see Grandfather.

690
00:37:21,400 --> 00:37:22,800
Ladies weren't supposed to attend

691
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:25,360
Crown Prince's
coming-of-age ceremony.

692
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:29,320
His Majesty gave his permission.

693
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,800
By attending his coming-of-age ceremony,

694
00:37:35,392 --> 00:37:37,616
you've made your relationship
known to everyone.

695
00:37:38,592 --> 00:37:40,070
You're leaving yourself no way out?

696
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:43,070
Do you really think

697
00:37:43,312 --> 00:37:45,712
I'm the kind of woman who
changes her affections on a whim?

698
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:51,590
My feelings for the Crown Prince

699
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:53,000
will never change.

700
00:37:54,144 --> 00:37:56,608
He could barely make it through
his coming-of-age ceremony.

701
00:37:57,030 --> 00:37:57,800
His health...

702
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,000
I know exactly

703
00:37:59,010 --> 00:38:00,790
what kind of condition
the Crown Prince is in.

704
00:38:30,070 --> 00:38:31,030
You have to let her go.

705
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:34,230
No matter how hard it is.

706
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,230
You want me to let go,

707
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:42,030
yet you yourself are obsessed with her.

708
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:50,480
I can't stand by and watch her

709
00:38:50,630 --> 00:38:51,800
marry someone else.

710
00:38:55,030 --> 00:38:55,880
Including you.

711
00:38:58,656 --> 00:39:00,400
I won't try to talk
you out of it anymore,

712
00:39:00,752 --> 00:39:02,704
and you don't need to
talk me out of it either.

713
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,360
Even if we are brothers,

714
00:39:07,110 --> 00:39:08,880
I won't give up the lady I love.

715
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:22,000
The Crown Prince isn't just frail.

716
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,360
He's smooth-talking, too.

717
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:24,670
He's hardly an ideal husband.

718
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,150
I can't stop worrying.

719
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:28,400
Will you please think it over again?

720
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,550
The men in northwest are too rough,

721
00:39:31,190 --> 00:39:33,110
and the men in the capital
are all smooth talkers.

722
00:39:33,232 --> 00:39:35,000
According to you, none
of them is any good.

723
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:37,030
Fine then.

724
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:38,550
Just take me back to northwest.

725
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,280
I'll never marry anyone.

726
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:43,320
You've never spoken
to me like this before.

727
00:39:43,670 --> 00:39:44,590
See?

728
00:39:44,688 --> 00:39:46,208
You're taking Crown Prince's side.

729
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,800
How has Father been these days?

730
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:58,880
Ever since you left,

731
00:39:59,030 --> 00:40:00,070
he's carried around

732
00:40:00,070 --> 00:40:02,280
the jade ring you used
to play with as a child.

733
00:40:02,336 --> 00:40:05,424
When he heard His Majesty and Empress
Dowager were choosing a husband for you,

734
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:06,480
he started preparing.

735
00:40:06,590 --> 00:40:09,070
He brought out the grape
wine he'd been aging for twelve years.

736
00:40:09,136 --> 00:40:09,880
As for your dowry,

737
00:40:10,110 --> 00:40:12,030
he prepared 300 cartloads.

738
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:14,590
He also reclaimed
100 qing of military farmland

739
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,280
along the Shule River.

740
00:40:16,710 --> 00:40:17,440
He said

741
00:40:18,230 --> 00:40:19,800
that when you finally marry,

742
00:40:19,936 --> 00:40:22,000
the sound of the golden
wheat swaying in the wind

743
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,630
would be the finest wedding music

744
00:40:23,630 --> 00:40:25,070
a father could offer his daughter.

745
00:40:25,510 --> 00:40:26,550
He also said

746
00:40:26,960 --> 00:40:28,190
that guarding northwest

747
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:29,510
is our duty,

748
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:32,190
the greatest dowry we can give you,

749
00:40:32,670 --> 00:40:34,190
and your strongest protection

750
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:36,550
and greatest support here in the palace.

751
00:40:39,150 --> 00:40:40,150
There's no one else

752
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:41,550
in this world

753
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:45,030
who loves his daughter
as much as Father does.

754
00:40:48,670 --> 00:40:49,550
Xihe,

755
00:40:50,190 --> 00:40:52,880
all we've ever wanted is
for you to live a carefree life

756
00:40:53,150 --> 00:40:55,030
and find someone to grow old with.

757
00:40:56,710 --> 00:40:57,880
But Crown Prince...

758
00:40:58,070 --> 00:40:59,030
I know.

759
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,190
Yun'an,

760
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,110
I'm all grown up now.

761
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:05,150
I know how to make my own choices

762
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:06,320
and what I need to do.

763
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:11,000
Xihe,

764
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,190
you really have changed.

765
00:41:14,384 --> 00:41:15,880
It's because heaven has blessed me,

766
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,504
and because I have a father and brother

767
00:41:17,630 --> 00:41:18,840
who love me so much,

768
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:20,510
that's why I can walk
the path I choose.

769
00:41:21,550 --> 00:41:22,920
So please don't worry about me.

770
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:24,710
Whatever I choose for myself,

771
00:41:25,150 --> 00:41:26,590
no matter what happens in the future,

772
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,110
I will have no regrets.

773
00:41:35,150 --> 00:41:35,710
By the way,

774
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:36,920
Yun'an,

775
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:39,400
I'm going to Fahua Temple
tomorrow to pray.

776
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:40,840
I'll go with you.

777
00:41:41,190 --> 00:41:42,840
I've made plans with Young Master Bu.

778
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:43,710
Don't worry.

779
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:45,880
That playboy?

780
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:47,840
You've gotten awfully close to him.

781
00:41:48,190 --> 00:41:50,150
Don't tell me he's
another one of your suitors.

782
00:41:53,550 --> 00:41:54,440
He's my best friend.

783
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:21,550
(I, Shen Xihe, pray for
peace in northwest.)

784
00:42:21,550 --> 00:42:23,840
(May the people be safe,
and my family protected.)

785
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:26,400
(And after marriage,)

786
00:42:26,464 --> 00:42:28,720
(may I walk hand in hand
with the Crown Prince,)

787
00:42:29,088 --> 00:42:31,216
(and may we live our
remaining years without regret.)

788
00:42:46,630 --> 00:42:47,230
Your Highness!

789
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,280
Xihe!

790
00:42:48,630 --> 00:42:49,400
I'm fine.

791
00:42:51,150 --> 00:42:51,880
Your Highness,

792
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:53,110
the wheel has broken.

793
00:42:53,230 --> 00:42:54,630
It'll take some time to repair it.

794
00:43:25,190 --> 00:43:25,920
Your Highness!

795
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:46,030
An Embroidered Envoy?

796
00:43:49,872 --> 00:43:52,190
So you're the coward who shot
that arrow from the shadows.

797
00:43:53,150 --> 00:43:53,710
Talk.

798
00:43:54,590 --> 00:43:55,880
Who sent you?

799
00:44:11,230 --> 00:44:13,880
Looks like I went too
easy on you last time.

800
00:44:14,016 --> 00:44:15,856
You clearly haven't learned your lesson.

801
00:44:15,872 --> 00:44:16,780
(Qing)
These are among

802
00:44:16,816 --> 00:44:18,670
the few remaining paintings
my wife left behind.

803
00:44:18,670 --> 00:44:20,000
♪A wall that collapses at a single push♪

804
00:44:20,000 --> 00:44:21,070
All burned.

805
00:44:21,110 --> 00:44:24,110
I did it so that you
wouldn't cling to any lingering hopes.

806
00:44:24,150 --> 00:44:26,480
(Qing)
Lest you do something outrageous again.

807
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:28,190
It's been so long.

808
00:44:32,710 --> 00:44:35,650
♪I've hidden so many words♪

809
00:44:36,270 --> 00:44:39,070
♪Too reluctant to tell you♪

810
00:44:39,940 --> 00:44:46,910
♪So never uncover♪

811
00:44:47,100 --> 00:44:49,460
♪The sand that slips away
with one grasp♪

812
00:44:50,590 --> 00:44:53,320
♪The flower that withers
after one bloom♪

813
00:44:54,280 --> 00:44:59,620
♪Silently buried deep inside my heart♪

814
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:04,200
♪Every answer I gave♪

815
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:07,850
♪Was both bittersweet and absurd♪

816
00:45:08,640 --> 00:45:12,010
♪Hiding my tear-filled eyes
when I hurt you♪

817
00:45:12,270 --> 00:45:15,580
♪How hard it truly was?♪

818
00:45:18,550 --> 00:45:21,990
♪The wounds that healed
with just a little comfort♪

819
00:45:22,980 --> 00:45:25,310
♪The lies made whole
with a single embrace♪

820
